The paper proposes a hybrid SDCA framework for multi-core clusters, which is a common high performance computing environment. The paper focuses on the optimization of loss functions, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
